column2: SELECT TOP # s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zwarning, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM GalSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE s.class = # AND s.zwarning = # ORDER BY s.fiberid
